Package com.munger.passwordkeeper.struct

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AES256
    Wrapper for the JNI AES and MD5 calls.
    PasswordDetails
    A struct that contains specific details for the PasswordDocument Details are composed of a name, URL or location, and key/value pairs associated with this location.
    PasswordDetails.Pair
    Key/Value pairs intrinsically linked to the base location of these details.
    PasswordDocument
    A data structure that contains a list of password details and information for encrypting to the file system.
